    "He'd run it through GPT-4, and it had solved everything.",
    "And some of the very most brilliant minds in my field do not speak English as a first language, and that has been a career handicap to so many people.",
    "And I am delighted that GPT-4 is now removing or reducing that obstacle to so many of my colleagues.",
